            <simpara>GT <replaceable role="entity">version</replaceable> release manuals are divided into the following areas:</simpara>
            <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem>
                                    <simpara>
                                                <emphasis role="strong">
                                                  <olink targetdoc="common">Common Runtime
                                                  Components</olink>
                                                </emphasis>
                                    </simpara>
                                    <simpara>These components include the WS Core (in
                                                Java, C and Python implementations) which is the
                                                foundation of GT4 web services components and
                                                provides a set of fundamental libraries and tools
                                                which are needed to build both WS and non-WS
                                                services in a grid. Includes information on GT4
                                                containers and clients that allow you to work with
                                                WS resources and resource properties. Also includes cross-component tools such
                                                as XIO (an extensible I/O library with drivers) and
                                                pyGlobus (a contribution that ...). Also a globus
                                                version of Java CoG kit and our common c libraries.</simpara>
