                        <listitem>
                                    <simpara>
                                                <emphasis role="strong">
                                                  <olink targetdoc="data">Data Management
                                                  Components</olink>
                                                </emphasis>
                                    </simpara>
                                    <simpara>Data management tools are concerned with the location, transfer, and management of distributed
                                                data. GT4 provides various basic tools, including GridFTP for high-performance and reliable data
                                                transport, RFT for managing multiple transfers, RLS for maintaining location information for
                                                replicated files, and OGSA-DAI for accessing and integrated structured and semistructured data. xxxxxxxalso mention ws rls and drsxxxxxxx.</simpara>
